"use client" import { useState, useEffect } from "react" import { useNavigate } from "react-router-dom" import { useAuth } from "../contexts/AuthContext" import { BarChart3, Clock, Target, TrendingUp, Play, ArrowLeft } from "lucide-react" import axios from "axios" import { API_BASE } from "../lib/config" export default function DashboardPage() { const navigate = useNavigate() const { currentUser } = useAuth() const [stats, setStats] = useState(null) const [loading, setLoading] = useState(true) useEffect(() => { const fetchStats = async () => { try { const response = await axios.get(`${API_BASE}/api/users/stats`) setStats(response.data) } catch (error) { console.error("Failed to fetch stats:", error) } finally { setLoading(false) } } fetchStats() }, []) if (loading) { return (
) } return (
{/* Header */}

Dashboard

Track your interview practice progress

{/* Stats Overview */}

Total Interviews

{stats?.totalInterviews || 0}

Completed

{stats?.completedInterviews || 0}

Average Score

{stats?.averageScore ? `${stats.averageScore.toFixed(1)}/10` : "N/A"}

Time Practiced

{stats?.totalTimeSpent ? `${Math.floor(stats.totalTimeSpent / 60)}h` : "0h"}

{/* Recent Interviews */}

Recent Interviews

{stats?.recentInterviews?.length > 0 ? (
{stats.recentInterviews.map((interview, index) => (

{interview.role}

{interview.experience} • {interview.difficulty} • {interview.duration} minutes

{new Date(interview.createdAt).toLocaleDateString()}

{interview.status}
{interview.overallScore && (

Score: {interview.overallScore}/10

)}
))}
) : (

No interviews yet

)}
) }
